docs.relocated_school_note_t: Chua Chu Kang Secondary School and Teck Whye Secondary School have merged in January 2023. The merged school name is Chua Chu Kang Secondary School and it will operate from both Chua Chu Kang Secondary School and Teck Whye Secondary School sites in 2023 and thereafter at the Teck Whye Secondary School site from 2024. NOTE: 2023 Secondary 1 students would attend school in Teck Whye Secondary School site from January 2023.
